Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:21.08,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}新的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:56.02,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs110\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}來自過去的禮物
